==Deletion of INA Jubilation image==
Hi, I deleted the INA jubilation image for two reasons. First there is already an image of Fujiwara and Mohan Singh, which I feel is more than adequate in depicting the significance that Mohan Singh holds in the INA story. Secondly, the image itself is pretty big, unsightly in the paragraph and does little to add to the article.It is also likely a staged photograph, as there is no record when where and how this image was taken. I am not aware of any joint INA-IJA operations or battles that ended in a victory or captured in photo. I hope that clarifies why I deleted the image.[[User:rueben_lys|rueben_lys]] ([[User talk:rueben_lys|talk]] '''·''' [[Special:Contribs/rueben_lys|contribs]]) 10:39, 1 October 2015 (UTC)
: Thanks for the clarification! --[[User:Mlewan|Mlewan]] ([[User talk:Mlewan|talk]]) 11:34, 1 October 2015 (UTC)
